{"tid":1450861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫推 聽日（12/8）1PM 機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:01:19.000Z","uid":69934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"078b811be21a1ca3a024b141df485fff04472b9e","tid":1450861,"uid":69934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:01:19.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0kg0OJa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0kg0OJa.png&h=26232685&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gYatc9R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgYatc9R.png&h=1d6198e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MCSSEPR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMCSSEPR.png&h=695c8cf9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vD9JMuR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvD9JMuR.png&h=3cae0cc7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8jzJMuS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8jzJMuS.png&h=74438c6d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4BbW6uS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4BbW6uS.png&h=d614e979&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QvDVCBx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQvDVCBx.png&h=d104b39b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TUKhQWy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2